item.title: CVE-2018-7511|2024-09-16T16:33:11.185Z -- eaton -- eaton%20elcsoft
item.description: In Eaton ELCSoft versions 2.04.02 and prior, there are multiple cases where specially crafted files could cause a buffer overflow which, in turn, may allow remote execution of arbitrary code.
